== AIAA 5037: Advanced Algorithms and Data Structures
~~~~~
{}{img_right}{slides/AIAA5037/course_cover.jpg}{Course Cover}{200}{}
~~~~~

=== Course Information
- **Instructor**: [https://sunyinggilly.github.io/ Ying Sun]
- **Email**: sunyinggilly@gmail.com
- **Office**: E1, 501b
- **Office Hours**: By appointment

=== Course Description
This course covers advanced topics in algorithms and data structures, including but not limited to:
- Advanced graph algorithms
- Dynamic programming techniques
- Computational geometry
- Approximation algorithms
- Randomized algorithms
- String algorithms

=== Prerequisites
- Data Structures and Algorithms
- Discrete Mathematics
- Programming proficiency in Python/C++

=== Textbooks
- *Introduction to Algorithms* (CLRS), 4th Edition
- *Algorithm Design* by Jon Kleinberg and Éva Tardos

=== Grading
- Assignments: 40%
- Midterm Exam: 20%
- Final Project: 40%

